      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. To be more specific, when these researchers talk about heritability and certain genetic markers, are they essentially suggesting a hierarchy of intelligence between different races? Like, do they lean towards certain groups being biologically predisposed to higher cognitive functions than others? I'm trying to see if the \"logic\" they use actually maps out a specific ranking.",
